{"tid":1124706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「新愛爾蘭共和軍」誤殺北愛爾蘭女記者麥基","createTime":"2019-04-25T07:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T07:51:58.000Z","uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fee9a6c117d5ecd15c1b839ec197932e51395c43","tid":1124706,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1454416-20190425.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1454416-20190425.htm&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=d301f8ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1454416-20190425.htm&h=26bb72c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1454416-20190425.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n北愛爾蘭女記者麥基在採訪北愛騷亂期間中槍身亡，喪禮在北愛首府貝爾法斯特一間教堂舉行，英國首相文翠珊、愛爾蘭總理瓦拉德卡等出席儀式。<br />\n<br />\n29歲的麥基上星期在倫敦德里採訪騷亂期間，中槍身亡，警方估計麥基是死於流彈。武裝組織「新愛爾蘭共和軍」承認是他們的成員的所為。<br />\n<br />\n警方一度拘捕三名男女，及後釋放。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲第一煩膠國加一分"}]}